INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4139','于成龙黄瓜籽粉招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的钙类类招商信息：<br><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">黄瓜籽粉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">是民间接骨、壮骨及补钙的最佳秘方。至今在农村小鸡腿折了、鸽子腿折了还喂黄瓜籽，几天腿就能接上了。缺钙引起腿抽筋的人，服用一代或半代就见效（<span lang=\"EN-US\">350</span>克包装）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">⑴经检验部门出据的检验报告，黄瓜籽含有大量的钙和磷及维生素，经加工炒熟后，易于人体吸收。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">⑵黄瓜籽粉对骨质疏松、腿脚抽筋、风湿病、关节炎、肩周炎、颈椎病及肝、胃、脾、肾等脏器疾病有恢复治疗与保健的功能<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span>中医说的“五痨”“七伤”并且调节人身体的协调与平衡，每百克黄瓜籽粉含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">89.9</span>毫克钙，<span lang=\"EN-US\">720</span>毫克的磷，其含有的钾盐、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>及微量元素、钙、铁，都能促进皮肤光洁柔肤。它能有效的促进人体钙的吸收，补钙的速度很快，补钙效果也是最佳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">⑶对长期劳伤和骨质损伤及股骨头坏死有恢复和治疗的功效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">⑷对人体疲劳过度有迅速恢复体力的功效。（有许多体育学院的教练给学生买黄瓜籽粉壮力）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">⑸有润肠治便秘的功效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:15pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\">食用方法及注意事项：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">⑴补钙一代食用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">10</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">天左右（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">350</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">克），一天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">2-3</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">次，一次</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">2-3</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">勺，如腿抽筋缺钙严重，最好多食用几袋，以提高人体的钙含量和免疫力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">⑵骨折、风湿病、股骨头坏死的人食用黄瓜籽同时，要食用生菜籽粉，一比一配着食用效果更好，一袋食用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">10</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">天左右。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">⑶可加入牛奶、豆浆、粥，也可直接冲服，但冲调后不成糊状，冲服后可有少许沉淀尽可放心食用，其含有丰富的膳食纤维。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">⑷因本产品有润肠之作用，儿童老人可酌减。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\"></span></p><br>符合长春市永龙食品有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
