INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4316','辣木片天瑞会销炒作招商代理 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的增强免疫力类招商信息：<br><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';color:#ff0000;font-size:12pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"> <p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">辣木营养学的三大特点：</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:-36pt;margin:0px 0px 0px 57.3pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;font-size:11pt;\"><span>1、<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#4f81bd;font-size:11pt;\">蛋白质含量高，不含胆固醇</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 36pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">人体大部份是由蛋白质组成， 【如需要，请上网搜：天瑞徐丽】蛋白质经人体消化后分解成氨基酸，再经由血液带到全身的组织。细胞各自选择所需氨基酸，以便制造新的生命组织、肌肉、</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 36pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">肠道、肝脏、肾脏等内脏器官，毛发、皮肤、骨骼中的基本成份，甚至酵素、荷尔蒙、血液中的血红素及免疫抗体等都有蛋白质构成。</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><br /></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">所有蛋白质的价值，视其中氨基酸含量而定。人体必需的八种氨基酸，为高品质的蛋白质食物，又称为完全蛋白质，这些蛋白质多含于蛋黄、鲜奶、肝脏</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 36pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">及肾脏等动物性食物中，比一般植物性蛋白质丰富。植物中除酵母、黄豆、谷类胚芽等含完全蛋白质外，其余植物所含必需氨基酸都是不完全蛋白质，无法单独维持人体健康。</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><br /></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">但令科学家惊奇的是，化验结果是在新鲜辣木树叶</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">6</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">．</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">7g/100g</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">所含的蛋白质超过菠菜</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">2</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">．</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">8g/100g</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">，两倍之多，而且含有的正是人体必备的八种氨基酸，为完全蛋白质。</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><br /></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">根据我们日常生活饮食所摄入的蛋白质主要是在动物蛋禽肉类中摄取，这些食物都含有较高量的油脂，对于有三高的患者来说是禁忌。鸡蛋的高胆固醇只存在动物性食物，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 36pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">植物性食物中所含的是化学构造和胆固醇相近的植物固醇，在人体内能防止胆固醇的沉积，所以辣木树可以说是</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">“</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">高蛋白质，零胆固醇</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">”</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">的食物。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:-36pt;margin:0px 0px 0px 57.3pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;font-size:11pt;\"><span>2、<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#4f81bd;font-size:11pt;\">丰富的各类矿物质</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#4f81bd;font-size:11pt;\"><br /></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">辣木树的矿物质包括钙、镁、磷、钾、铜、铁、硫。其中每一百公克新鲜辣木树叶的钙质为</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">440mg</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">，是相同重量牛奶钙质</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">120mg</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">的四倍；每一百公克新鲜的辣木树叶的</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 36pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">铁含量为</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">7mg</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">，是相同重量波菜铁</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">2</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">．</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">1mg</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">的三倍多，所以食用辣木树产品，就能补充我们生活中容易欠缺的矿物质。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:-36pt;margin:0px 0px 0px 57.3pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;font-size:11pt;\"><span>3、<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#4f81bd;font-size:11pt;\">含量高的维生素</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 36pt;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">社会经济发展和进步，人们的饮食型态有相当大的改变，而到底现代人的饮食状况如何</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">?&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">还有营养素缺乏的现象吗</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">?&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">而根据现实的状况及很多调查资料显示，现代人在脂肪与糖类</span></p><p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;widows:2;text-transform:none;background-color:#ffffff;text-indent:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font:14px/24px tahoma, arial, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', 宋体;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;color:#333333;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">摄取过多，但维生素与矿物质摄取不均衡，其中维生素</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">B1</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">、</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">B2</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">、</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">B6</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">、</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">E</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">的平均摄取量极容易低于正常值。</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:punctuation;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><br /></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:宋体;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">健康的身体来自营养的均衡，辣木树潜藏丰富的维生素，可以补足日常我们容易欠缺的营养素。</span></p></span><br>符合威海天瑞生物技术有限公司1代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
